(4, 7, '<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/130501/1-130501201Fb05.jpg" style="width: 701px; height: 652px;" /><br />\r\n<ul style="list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(126, 46, 31); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 22.986112594604492px; background-color: rgb(248, 243, 237);">\r\n	几乎每个人都有这样的经历，在舌尖放上一小块巧克力，然后闭上眼睛， 感觉着它柔缓、细腻融化的时候，一些甜蜜、欣悦或者忧伤、惆怅的 情绪，也缓缓从心底释放出来，越来越浓，越来越让自己感动\r\n	<li>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n		<ul>\r\n			<li style="list-style: none; margin: 0px 170px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top; float: left; line-height: 35px; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; letter-spacing: 1.1111111640930176px;">\r\n				<strong>食材:</strong>比利时巧克力，牙买加朗姆酒。</li>\r\n			<li style="list-style: none; margin: 0px 170px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top; float: left; line-height: 35px; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; letter-spacing: 1.1111111640930176px;">\r\n				<strong>最佳食用温度:</strong>5℃</li>\r\n			<li style="list-style: none; margin: 0px 170px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top; float: left; line-height: 35px; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; letter-spacing: 1.1111111640930176px;">\r\n				<strong>最佳存放条件:</strong>5℃存放24小时</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '', '127.0.0.1'),
(2, 6, '<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/130501/1-130501200031E4.jpg" style="width: 703px; height: 672px;" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<ul style="list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(126, 46, 31); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 23px; background-color: rgb(248, 243, 237);">\r\n	记忆回到那古老的小镇，徘徊在十八世纪建筑之间的狭窄街道上，视线 穿越鹅卵石铺成的小街两旁那盏古老的风灯，想起了和她的故事\r\n	<li>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n		<ul>\r\n			<li style="list-style: none; margin: 0px 170px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top; float: left; line-height: 35px; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n				<strong>食材:</strong>德国淡奶油，澳大利亚黄油，炒制过的新鲜苹果，韩国幼砂糖。</li>\r\n			<li style="list-style: none; margin: 0px 170px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top; float: left; line-height: 35px; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n				<strong>最佳食用温度:</strong>5℃</li>\r\n			<li style="list-style: none; margin: 0px 170px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top; float: left; line-height: 35px; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n				<strong>最佳存放条件:</strong>5℃存放24小时</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style="list-style: none; margin: 0px 170px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top; float: left; line-height: 35px; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '', '127.0.0.1'),
(5, 8, '<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/130501/1-1305012020412Z.jpg" style="width: 701px; height: 663px;" /><br />\r\n<ul style="list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(126, 46, 31); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 22.986112594604492px; background-color: rgb(248, 243, 237);">\r\n	浓香奶酪与水果的甜蜜对话，独特的味道带给你美国乡村的感受\r\n	<li>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n		<ul>\r\n			<li style="list-style: none; margin: 0px 170px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top; float: left; line-height: 35px; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; letter-spacing: 1.1111111640930176px;">\r\n				<strong>食材:</strong>法国天然奶油，澳大利亚奶油芝士，口味厚重。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n			<li style="list-style: none; margin: 0px 170px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top; float: left; line-height: 35px; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; letter-spacing: 1.1111111640930176px;">\r\n				<strong>最佳食用温度:</strong>5℃</li>\r\n			<li style="list-style: none; margin: 0px 170px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top; float: left; line-height: 35px; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; letter-spacing: 1.1111111640930176px;">\r\n				<strong>最佳存放条件:</strong>5℃存放24小时</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '', '127.0.0.1'),
(3, 7, '<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/130501/1-13050120130A59.jpg" style="width: 703px; height: 644px;" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<ul style="list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(126, 46, 31); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 22.986112594604492px; background-color: rgb(248, 243, 237);">\r\n	融合了樱桃的酸、奶油的甜、巧克力的苦、 樱桃酒的醇香。完美的黑森林蛋糕 经得起各种口味的挑剔。\r\n	<li>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n		<ul>\r\n			<li style="list-style: none; margin: 0px 170px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top; float: left; line-height: 35px; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; letter-spacing: 1.1111111640930176px;">\r\n				<strong>食材:</strong>比利时苦甜巧克力，黑樱桃，樱桃白兰地。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n			<li style="list-style: none; margin: 0px 170px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top; float: left; line-height: 35px; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; letter-spacing: 1.1111111640930176px;">\r\n				<strong>最佳食用温度:</strong>5℃</li>\r\n			<li style="list-style: none; margin: 0px 170px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top; float: left; line-height: 35px; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; letter-spacing: 1.1111111640930176px;">\r\n				<strong>最佳存放条件:</strong>5℃存放24小时</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '', '127.0.0.1'),
(6, 8, '<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/130501/1-13050120215L14.jpg" style="width: 703px; height: 668px;" /><br />\r\n<ul style="list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(126, 46, 31); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 22.986112594604492px; background-color: rgb(248, 243, 237);">\r\n	口感爽滑细腻，没有一丝甜腻，原汁原味的欧式工艺，给你香醇自然的奶酪之旅。\r\n	<li>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n		<ul>\r\n			<li style="list-style: none; margin: 0px 170px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top; float: left; line-height: 35px; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; letter-spacing: 1.1111111640930176px;">\r\n				<strong>食材:</strong>德国淡奶油，澳大利亚奶油芝士，韩国幼砂糖，口感酸甜，奶香浓郁。</li>\r\n			<li style="list-style: none; margin: 0px 170px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top; float: left; line-height: 35px; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; letter-spacing: 1.1111111640930176px;">\r\n				<strong>最佳食用温度:</strong>5℃</li>\r\n			<li style="list-style: none; margin: 0px 170px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top; float: left; line-height: 35px; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; letter-spacing: 1.1111111640930176px;">\r\n				<strong>最佳存放条件:</strong>5℃存放24小时</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '', '127.0.0.1'),
(7, 9, '<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/130501/1-13050120240T41.jpg" style="width: 693px; height: 562px;" /><br />\r\n<ul style="list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(126, 46, 31); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 23px; background-color: rgb(248, 243, 237);">\r\n	如果你爱上了一个人，只要给对方一块提拉米苏，就意味着将心交到爱 人手中，愿与其远走天涯，所以才有人说：提拉米苏的味道是开启爱情 的钥匙，是从红尘走向天堂的滋味。带一个人，陪一段爱，远走天涯吧！\r\n	<li>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n		<ul>\r\n			<li style="list-style: none; margin: 0px 170px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top; float: left; line-height: 35px; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n				<strong>食材:</strong>意大利玛斯卡波尼芝士，肯尼亚咖啡，法国可可粉。</li>\r\n			<li style="list-style: none; margin: 0px 170px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top; float: left; line-height: 35px; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n				<strong>最佳食用温度:</strong>5℃</li>\r\n			<li style="list-style: none; margin: 0px 170px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top; float: left; line-height: 35px; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n				<strong>最佳存放条件:</strong>5℃存放24小时</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<br />\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '', '127.0.0.1'),
